## chart main Swimmers Project Status Crux
```mermaid
flowchart LR
  vision["swimmers: visual tmux aquarium, thought rail, and browser cockpit for parallel agents"]:::gray
  core["GREEN Rust API plus native TUI aquarium and thought bridge shipped"]:::green
  web["GREEN web Trogdor cockpit terminal sheets islands with Node web tests and Web CI gate"]:::green
  fleet["GREEN remote multi-SSH fleet environments and operator-pressure atlas"]:::green
  release["GREEN v0.3.0 tagged curl-sh installer macOS-arm64 plus Linux prebuilt binaries"]:::green
  crates["RED cargo install swimmers still planned crate not published to crates.io no open bead"]:::red
  next["Next move cut 0.3.x for unreleased Web-CI work or publish crate"]:::gray
  vision --> core --> web --> fleet --> release
  release --> crates --> next
  class vision gray
  class core green
  class web green
  class fleet green
  class release green
  class crates red
  class next gray
  classDef green fill:#dff7df,stroke:#20833a,stroke-width:2px,color:#0f2f18
  classDef yellow fill:#fff3bf,stroke:#b7791f,stroke-width:2px,color:#3a2a00
  classDef red fill:#ffd6d6,stroke:#c53030,stroke-width:2px,color:#3a0505
  classDef gray fill:#eef2f7,stroke:#64748b,stroke-width:1px,color:#111827
```

