## chart lifecycle Swimmers Session Lifecycle
```mermaid
flowchart TD
  spawn["GREEN discover or adopt tmux session"]:::green
  idle["GREEN idle state fish dozing"]:::green
  active["GREEN active swimming from pane activity"]:::green
  busy["GREEN busy bubbling high token throughput"]:::green
  attention["GREEN attention or error x-eyes needs operator"]:::green
  evidence["GREEN state_evidence marks observed vs stale or inferred"]:::green
  input["GREEN operator input or group-input batch response"]:::green
  sleep["GREEN drowsy sleeping deep-sleep exited"]:::green
  spawn --> idle --> active --> busy --> attention
  attention --> input --> active
  active --> sleep
  busy --> evidence
  attention --> evidence
  class spawn green
  class idle green
  class active green
  class busy green
  class attention green
  class evidence green
  class input green
  class sleep green
  classDef green fill:#dff7df,stroke:#20833a,stroke-width:2px,color:#0f2f18
  classDef yellow fill:#fff3bf,stroke:#b7791f,stroke-width:2px,color:#3a2a00
  classDef red fill:#ffd6d6,stroke:#c53030,stroke-width:2px,color:#3a0505
```

## chart architecture-boundary Swimmers Architecture Boundary
```mermaid
flowchart TD
  tmux["GRAY tmux the only external dependency"]:::gray
  api["GREEN Rust API server supervisor session discovery"]:::green
  inproc["GREEN InProcessApi embedded mode single swimmers-tui binary"]:::green
  tui["GREEN native TUI ratatui aquarium client"]:::green
  web["GREEN web surface axum static assets plus WS sessions"]:::green
  store["GREEN file-based JSON persistence no database no Docker"]:::green
  metrics["GREEN Prometheus GET metrics auth-protected"]:::green
  remote["GREEN remote-sessions proxy and SSH-only handoff targets"]:::green
  tmux --> api
  api --> inproc --> tui
  api --> web
  api --> store
  api --> metrics
  api --> remote
  class tmux gray
  class api green
  class inproc green
  class tui green
  class web green
  class store green
  class metrics green
  class remote green
